<section id="Immediately_Retiring_an_Instance" remap="TID_22233">
	<title>Immediately Retiring an Instance</title>
	<para> 
		<productname>CloudForms Management Engine</productname> allows you to retire an instance immediately.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Immediately Retire an Instance</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				From <menuchoice><guimenu>Clouds</guimenu><guisubmenu>Instances</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, click on the instance that you want to remove the retirement date from.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2007.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> (<guilabel>Lifecycle</guilabel>).
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2010.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> (<guilabel>Retire Selected Items</guilabel>).
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
	<formalpara>
		<title>Result:</title>
		<para>
			The instance is immediately stopped and cannot restart.
		</para>
	</formalpara>
</section>